q","Hampstead and Kilburn","Tulip Siddiq","49313"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/604772","Department for Education","false","2016-11-02","<p>The information required to answer this question is not held and compiling it would be a very complex task which would incur disproportionate cost.</p>","Bognor Regis and Littlehampton","Nick Gibb",,"2016-11-02T17:47:02.067Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/604772/answer","Biography information for Nick Gibb","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/604772/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/604772/answer",,,,,"60","Education","Education","2016-10-18","Grammar Schools: Disadvantaged","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Education, how many children in receipt of free school meals dropped out of grammar schools in each selective and partially-selective education authority area in the most recent year for which data is available.","false","Biography information for Lucy Powell","Manchester Central","Lucy Powell","49287"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/604773","Department for Education","false","2016-11-02","<p>The Department for Education does not collect data on whether those pupils sitting the entrance exam for a selective school are eligible for free school meals; neither are local authorities required to provide this information to the Department.</p>","Bognor Regis and Littlehampton","Nick Gibb",,"2016-11-02T17:52:54.69Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/604773/answer","Biography information for Nick Gibb","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/604773/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/604773/answer",,,,,"60","Education","Education","2016-10-18","Grammar Schools: Disadvantaged","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Education, how many and what proportion of children in receipt of free school meals (a) sat and (b) passed the 11-plus exam in each fully and partially-selective local education authority area in the most recent year for which data is available.","false","Biography information for Lucy Powell","Manchester Central","Lucy Powell","49288"
